  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Kill Me If You Can: Single-Player Version</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We recommend searching for and enjoying <strong>Kill Me If You Can: Multiplayer Edition</strong> as well.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight with massive zombies, chain explosions, and characters that can be controlled at the same time in a fast and dynamic battle. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > If you pride yourself on being a skilled player in the RTS and AOS genres with fast and precise controls, multitasking, and quick decision-making skills, give it a try. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Can you really survive even for a day?  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >1. Characters</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2878230/extras/4db323a9511f5f6a1ec5d8709981732d.poster.avif?t=1733505066\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2878230/extras/4db323a9511f5f6a1ec5d8709981732d.webm?t=1733505066\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2878230/extras/4db323a9511f5f6a1ec5d8709981732d.mp4?t=1733505066\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Play with multiple characters, each with unique roles and three distinct skills. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Control up to three characters simultaneously for strategic gameplay. </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >2. Items</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2878230/extras/39d67953d1caad1a8cf16bc17ee9c3cd.poster.avif?t=1733505066\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2878230/extras/39d67953d1caad1a8cf16bc17ee9c3cd.webm?t=1733505066\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2878230/extras/39d67953d1caad1a8cf16bc17ee9c3cd.mp4?t=1733505066\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Explore various items such as regular, special, obstacles, and equipment. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Combine items strategically for maximum effectiveness. </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >3. Maps</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2878230/extras/78fa3405435df9fcab800f1c995f4b92.poster.avif?t=1733505066\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2878230/extras/78fa3405435df9fcab800f1c995f4b92.webm?t=1733505066\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2878230/extras/78fa3405435df9fcab800f1c995f4b92.mp4?t=1733505066\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Experience day and night cycles in Kill Me If You Can. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Explore the world by day, focusing on growth and farming efficiently. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > The world is divided into eight unique zones. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > At night, utilize farmed items to build defenses against hordes of incoming zombies.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Kill Me If You Can: Single-Player Version</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We recommend searching for and enjoying <strong>Kill Me If You Can: Multiplayer Edition</strong> as well.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight with massive zombies, chain explosions, and characters that can be controlled at the same time in a fast and dynamic battle. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > If you pride yourself on being a skilled player in the RTS and AOS genres with fast and precise controls, multitasking, and quick decision-making skills, give it a try. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Can you really survive even for a day?  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >1. Characters</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2878230/extras/4db323a9511f5f6a1ec5d8709981732d.poster.avif?t=1733505066\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2878230/extras/4db323a9511f5f6a1ec5d8709981732d.webm?t=1733505066\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2878230/extras/4db323a9511f5f6a1ec5d8709981732d.mp4?t=1733505066\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Play with multiple characters, each with unique roles and three distinct skills. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Control up to three characters simultaneously for strategic gameplay. </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >2. Items</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2878230/extras/39d67953d1caad1a8cf16bc17ee9c3